# 🌍 EcoVoyage – Sustainable Travel Planner v2

A structured, step-by-step full-stack Flask application for sustainable travel planning.

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
# Open http://localhost:5050
```

